Study Finds That Poor White Americans Still Benefit From White Privilege

Reported by April V. Taylor

Upward social and economic mobility has long been heralded as the cornerstone of the American Dream, the crowning achievement for anyone willing to work hard enough. However, this notion that America is a meritocracy has been proven to be a falsehood once again.
